    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is an uncompromising E46 M3 in collector-grade condition. This example features the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, characterized by its individual throttle bodies and precise double-VANOS variable valve timing. The drivetrain is paired with a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M Variable Differential Lock for superior mechanical grip. This vehicle has undergone rigorous preventative maintenance, including subframe reinforcement and rod bearing replacement, ensuring the structural integrity of the chassis and the longevity of the rotating assembly. The suspension maintains its factory-spec geometry with fresh bushings, providing telepathic feedback. The exterior finish and interior ergonomics remain in showroom state, reflecting a life of climate-controlled storage and fastidious mechanical care.",
