      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in Laguna Seca Blue. This specimen features the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, equipped with individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline, mated to a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox. The mechanical integrity is superlative: the VANOS system has been overhauled with Beisan components, rod bearings have been replaced as a preventative measure, and the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced. The chassis retains its factory-spec rigidity, supported by an M-Variable limited-slip differential and flawless suspension kinematics. With original paint depth and an interior free of typical bolster wear or pixel degradation, this is a turn-key example for the collector demanding peak longitudinal and lateral performance.",
